The paper deals with signal processing tasks in the physical layer of next-generation communication systems, specifically in the context of filter bank-based multicarrier (FBMC) systems. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Communications (cs.COMM), and Signal Processing (cs.SI) sub-categories.
